  29 Aug 2008; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org>
  +files/ruby-1.8.6_p287-entity_expansion_limit.diff,
  +ruby-1.8.6_p287-r1.ebuild:
  Fix REXML security issues, bug #236060.

