*ruby-1.6.8-r6 (30 Jan 2004)
*ruby-1.8.0-r5 (30 Jan 2004)
*ruby-1.8.1-r1 (30 Jan 2004)

  30 Jan 2004; Mamoru KOMACHI <usata@gentoo.org> ruby-1.6.8-r6.ebuild,
  ruby-1.8.0-r5.ebuild, ruby-1.8.1-r1.ebuild:
